{
  "stem": "10181.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, they-- they considered the Dutch to be kinsmen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there even was an occasion where-- and this is sort of-- I always-- always remember this where-- I don't know whether it was-- I don't think it was-- I think it was just a regular soldier who was giving us candy or something.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one of the boys said to me, you don't want to give it to him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He's a Jew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, so the soldier turned around to him and said, I didn't ask you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't ask your opinion, you know, which was sort of-- was very strange.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, but at the time, sort of, I took it in stride.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, I thought it was very nice of him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But this was just the first week or two, you know, when they were that civilized.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, and then-- first of all, after a few days, the Gestapo-- Gestapo is the German secret police.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They knocked on the door to look for my uncle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And of course, he was gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Like he knew-- he knew that they would look for him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had taken his bicycle and had-- took the-- and was going into Holland, deeper into Holland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, he-- he thought maybe he could out-cycle the German army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, like-- like everybody, nobody realized that, you know, that Holland would very quickly capitulate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was cycling in the direction of the-- the interior provinces.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or I would say Holland-- Holland itself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, like the-- like Amsterdam or this area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And supposedly-- and this he told me again many years later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Supposedly, the Dutch, their defense was the dikes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They would make holes in the dikes and Holland would be underwater.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
